{"tid":110823,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得啲女話要留住個處好撚虛偽?","createTime":"2017-02-07T03:47:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-07T14:26:04.000Z","uid":75870,"like":46,"dislike":193,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dfac0c88e38984fc75744513c0fe155e99a590f4","tid":110823,"uid":75870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T03:47:19.000Z","msg":"我同你拍緊拖，有性好合情合理啊，唔扑你唔通扑你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但啲女又好Q多籍口，聽得最多就係要留番結婚先。<br />\n<br />\n我屌咩戇撚鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 根本就係吊高黎賣，仲要扮清高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先，當我係條仔，你話個處留番比未來老公唔比我扑，咁即係當我水魚啦? 如果你認真當我係未來伴侶，點解唔比我扑而要等簽左張紙先?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其次，結左婚一樣可以離婚，我簽完紙屌完你一獲就離婚你吹鳩我漲咩傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就算無咁誇，你將個處當獎勵品咁交易好高清咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢啲女根本係用個處黎騎牛搵馬，仲要懶係野咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成日話咩物化女性，根本係自己物化自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔想扑野唯一可以接受既原因係驚生bb/生理問題，其他都可以塞番落佢個閪到。<br />\n<br />\n如果你條女用呢個理由唔比屌唔該你立即屌醒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓豬屌得好<br />\n負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓豬屌得好 不過我唔同意"},{"pid":"6a9d57b03e60a5c30b529e6c6963909eaaa7b034","tid":110823,"uid":82931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T03:49:46.000Z","msg":"樓主精蟲上腦"},{"pid":"96c56958185c58be5b7dd890b73f8959dd608852","tid":110823,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T03:50:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/a